Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.82,0:22:27.35,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}才能变得甘甜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.35,0:22:30.62,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}还是会枯萎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.69,0:22:34.08,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我想要知道我的未来
